ubiome inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Health Care
Industry: Health Care Facilities & Svcs
Sub-Industry: Health Care Services
uBiome Inc. provides public access to DNA sequencing technology to understand the microbiome. The Company offers investigate personal microbiome and learn how to correlate with others, and provides its sample kits online.




